docs.snippet: LEAD:  GOLF  Jersey Wins Dodge Cup: The New Jersey section of the Professional Golfers Association captured the sixth annual Dodge Challenge Cup over the Met section of the P.G.A. in a one-hole sudden-death playoff yesterday at Rockaway River Country...
docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: GOLF Jersey Wins Dodge Cup: The New Jersey section of the Professional Golfers Association captured the sixth annual Dodge Challenge Cup over the Met section of the P.G.A. in a one-hole sudden-death playoff yesterday at Rockaway River Country Club at Denville, N.J. The two eight-player teams were tied at 72 points after a 27-hole format that included best-ball, alternate-shot and singles matches.

docs.snippet: LEAD: The United States will put forward in Geneva this week a plan to phase out many American farm programs if other countries agree to similar cutbacks. The offer is part of negotiations to end trade distortion in agriculture by the next century.
